text: Edgecombe County is a county in the U.S. state of North Carolina. At the 2020 Census, its population was 48,900. Its county seat is Tarboro. Edgecombe County is part of the Rocky Mount, North Carolina Metropolitan Statistical Area. ==References== Category:1740s establishments in North Carolina Category:1741 establishments in the Thirteen Colonies Category:North Carolina counties
